.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-CANCEL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-cancel \- cancel a pending BOLT-11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-cancel
.I label
.SH DESCRIPTION
Cancels a pending (unpaid) BOLT-11 invoice by its label via
.BR delinvoice .
Only unpaid invoices can be cancelled; paid or expired invoices
will return an error.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"label":"..."}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-create (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-status (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1)
